who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE224\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE224\">DE224</a></td><td>EnceVir</td><td>EnceVir vaccine product, which is a vaccine for TBE</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE225</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE225\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE225\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 3 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE225-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE226\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE226\">DE226</a></td><td>Typbar-TCV</td><td>Typbar typhoid conjugate vaccine (Typbar-TCV)</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE225-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE227\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE227\">DE227</a></td><td>ViPS</td><td>Vi polysaccharide (ViPS) vaccine</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE225-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE228\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE228\">DE228</a></td><td>Ty21a</td><td>Ty21a vaccine</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE229</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE229\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE229\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 2 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE229-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE230\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE230\">DE230</a></td><td>WC vaccine</td><td>Killed whole-cell (WC) only cholera vaccine</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE229-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE231\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE231\">DE231</a></td><td>WC-rBS vaccine</td><td>Vaccine contains a mixture of the recombinant B subunit (rBS) of cholera toxin plus killed WC</td></tr></table><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>ValueSet #IMMZ.D.DE232</b></p><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE232\"> </a><a name=\"hcQIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE232\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 4 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE232-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE233\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE233\">DE233</a></td><td>MenA conjugate vaccine (5µg)</td><td>Monovalent serogroup A (MenA) conjugate vaccine (5µg)</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE232-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE234\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.D.html#IMMZ.D-DE234\">DE234</a></td><td>Monovalent MenC conjugate</td><td>Monovalent MenC conjugate vaccine</td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"QIMMZD1/IMMZ.D.DE232-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D-DE235\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ